text:
Hello, I am trying to get line item images to appear in an email rich text module. This is the code that I have used thus far:
```&lt;p&gt;
{% email_each list="deal.line_items" item="line_item" image="hs_images"%}

&lt;div style="display: flex; flex-direction:column; width: fit-content; margin: 45px 0"&gt;
  &lt;span&gt;Product: {{line_item.name}} Quantity: {{line_item.quantity}} Quantity Total: {{ line.item.quantity|multiply(line_item.price)|format(`currency`) }}&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; height: 110px;"&gt;

  &lt;img class="line-items__image" "img src={{line_item.hs_images}}" style="max-width: 100%; max-height" /&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;
{% endemail_each %}
 &lt;/p&gt;```
Do you have any suggestions to get the image to appear?
